Common.Highlight.Common.Text: TRIPLE NET LEASE TO ASX LISTED TENANT

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE Freestanding Retail Investments & CBRE Victorian Development Sites is pleased to present for your consideration the ‘Preston Toyota Site’, a land-rich intergenerational investment with unrivalled future development scope in Melbourne’s highly sought after inner north.

The property is best described as follows:

+Strategic 1.48ha* premium gateway corner site

+Triple street frontage to High Street (103m*), Regent Street (99m*) and William Street (25m*)

+Established quality improvements comprising 4,700sqm* motor vehicle showrooms, spare parts showroom/store, service centre, carwash and large hardstand area

+Leased to ASX listed Eagers Automotive (ASX:APE) with a market cap of over $4.2Billion.

+Strong net income of $1,082,345 p.a.* plus 3.5% annual increases

+Priority Development Zone (PDZ) promoting high density development (STCA).

+Positioned within Preston’s activity centre, only 250m* to Regent Train Station, 500m* to Woolworths & 600m* to Preston Market.

For Sale Via International Expressions of Interest Closing Thursday 23rd September 2021 at 2:00PM (AEST)

Set amongst an active and growing part of Melbourne, this property presents a great opportunity for boutique apartment developers.

•  Permit approved for 6 Storey Development
•  Development Site area of 711sqm*
•  Priority Development Zone
•  Moments from High Street retail amenity, including the well known Preston Market
•  Immediate access to Public Transport (Train, Tram & Bus Services)

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: LAND RICH CORNER INVESTMENT FULLY LEASED TO RENOWNED RETAILER (4 STORES IN VICTORIA)

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer 28-44 Albert Street, Preston, available for sale via Expressions of Interest closing Thursday 7th September 2017 at 3pm (AEST).

Located within the metropolitan fringe location of Preston, this rare development opportunity is situated amongst a diverse range of surrounding uses such as retail, office, industrial and residential.

The property is located 11km* north of the Melbourne CBD and provides exceptional access to major road arterials such as Bell Street, St Georges Road and Sydney Road.

The vacant industrial land parcel provides the following key features:
+ Two significant street frontages (Albert Street & Daley Street)
+Over 12,000 cars pass the site each day
+ Potential for office / industrial / large format retail (STCA)
+ Rare opportunity in flexible Industrial 3 Zone
+ Site area: 13,590sqm*

For further information regarding this opportunity or to arrange an inspection of the property, kindly contact CBRE.

Expressions of Interest Closing Thursday 7th September 2017 at 3pm (AEST)

*approx.
